modName: Level 1 Nord - Major questlines finished - No mods used
summary: This is my save where I've completed all of the major quest lines including the DLC's.
descriptionHtml:
[b]Requirements[/b]: 
TES V: Skyrim v1.9 or higher
DLC: Dawnguard
DLC: Dragonborn
DLC: Hearthfire

[b]Description[/b]:
This is my save file of a female nord that I've not leveled. I've used speed cheat and sometimes the kill command and also god mode. I just upload this file so I can access it for mod testing without having to go through some of the major quests again but I figured someone else might have use for it so I upload it here.

No points have been added so the character is still level 1. The name of the character is Test and she owns one property which is the Lakeview manor. However only the small building is built so you can still customize the house to your liking. Also inside the Lakeview manor you'll find all items inside the chest (except for quests items, they are in inventory).

For those that don't know how to change or re-customize your character: Use console command " ~ " key and type showracemenu


[b]Quests completed[/b]:
Main
Thieves Guild
Nightingale
Collage of Winterhold
Dawnguard - Dawnguard path
Dragonborn

And for the rest check the quest menu for things I've done and quest activated. 


Install:
Put the save files into your save file folder. (Documents/My Games/Skyrim/Saves)


Uninstall:
Delete the files/folders associated with the mod.
author: Spireaine
